Install cross compiler: 
    git clone https://github.com/lordmilko/i686-elf-tools
    cd i686-elf-tools
    ./i686-elf-tools.sh linux
    unzip /usr/local


    1. Boot code asm

    2. Kernel main

    3. Linker

    4. Grub

    5. Makefile 



